 src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FgJ3AAzs8alcH0yzvjc5szHnH-KE\"><br></p>\n<p>体验：<iframe src=\"https://ide.codemao.cn/we/559531\" width=\"640\" height=\"498\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></iframe></p>\n<p>我还将在发现里发布《平方差（未完成）》的作品，大家购买后可以自己锻炼拼接。</p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1492322223,"created_at":1492322223,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"18964","user":{"id":"179233","nickname":"杰鸽","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/Fj9WL32g3J_9Om1sWroOWquXZ25U","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>继上文</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/Fm1wqfeBABhtcN1_CPzWlZT8zs5D\"><br></p>\n<p>真嘚瑟！</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/Fva7P8X84yvKNsrZtOFHKgPUnx2k\"><br></p>\n<p>重头戏来啦！</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FshrHtsPc4dUccqF_eZagzkyDNwX\"><br></p>\n<p>啊不对有BUG！</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FgOEKMcPCAc7gXfNsdnZ02XN8--c\"><br></p>\n<p>这就对啦！</p>\n<p>高级的计算机知道你叫什么名字。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FtsRa6DUF0v_ogDG1xx1G4_aiZNM\"><br></p>\n<p>不要忘记加标点。</p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1492321781,"created_at":1492321781,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"18956","user":{"id":"179233","nickname":"杰鸽","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/Fj9WL32g3J_9Om1sWroOWquXZ25U","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>设置变量....</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FoefJrxonI-82MrMFBlULPOmFAj_\"><br></p>\n<p>开始编写！</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FsVgU1GbFLr3bxpJ4NbVI5def-Q8\"><br></p>\n<p>不要忘了加标点！</p>\n<p><br></p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1492321486,"created_at":1492321486,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"18952","user":{"id":"179233","nickname":"杰鸽","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/Fj9WL32g3J_9Om1sWroOWquXZ25U","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>打开创作平台：把所有东西都删了，只留下炫酷BGM</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/Foo2o_4Yo98cugfsP5w-ihmKGdhS\"><br></p>\n<p>然后，找一个或画一个运算角色以及一个背景（我找了滑稽）</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FjQNDFhxGYrerbhxbCNldaskV0YX\"><br></p>\n<p>然后就可以写代码了(不老实没百度的看——平方差公式：a²-b²=（a+b）×(a-b))</p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1492321165,"created_at":1492321165,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"18947","user":{"id":"179233","nickname":"杰鸽","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/Fj9WL32g3J_9Om1sWroOWquXZ25U","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>【<strong>编程小技巧】</strong></p>\n<p><strong>教大家做《超级计算机》！</strong></p>\n<p><strong>1.随便想一个公式（我们这次先做平方差公式的计算机）</strong></p>\n<p><strong>不知道</strong><strong>平方差公式的自行百度</strong><iframe src=\"https://www.baidu.com\" width=\"640\" height=\"498\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></iframe></p>\n<p><br></p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1492320709,"created_at":1492320709,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"18942","user":{"id":"179233","nickname":"杰鸽","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/Fj9WL32g3J_9Om1sWroOWquXZ25U","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>@技术猫</p>\n<p>是不是发了课的都可以上<a rel=\"nofollow\"></a><a href=\"https://codemao.gitbooks.io/block/content/\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://codemao.gitbooks.io/block/content/</a>？</p>\n<p><br></p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1492320429,"created_at":1492320429,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"18941","user":{"id":"179233","nickname":"杰鸽","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/Fj9WL32g3J_9Om1sWroOWquXZ25U","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>继上文</p>\n<p>15.<img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FsE510Jdz-lrVJBLc0HBxObdttdi\"><br></p>\n<p>分析：顾名思义，使用此积木可以让角色被鼠标操作到某一位置。拼图游戏经常用到。看看这个：<iframe src=\"https://ide.codemao.cn/we/254252\" width=\"640\" height=\"498\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></iframe></p>\n<p>这里的每一块拼图都用了该积木。随便看一块拼图脚本：<img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FgfsxRftoVcjoQrcNZMVxSEaaTEj\"></p>\n<p>看到了吧！</p>\n<p>--------------------------------完结--------------------------------------------------------------------</p>\n<p>最后留一个随堂测验，请萌新们做出本次课堂用到了的作品。（当然，不做也是可以的）</p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1492320334,"created_at":1492320334,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"18939","user":{"id":"179233","nickname":"杰鸽","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/Fj9WL32g3J_9Om1sWroOWquXZ25U","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>继上文</p>\n<p>13.14</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FuNa9QIfvkPRiI3ZK5Njv6YySDOj\"></p>\n<p>强调徐徐上升，或下降，动作看上去自然。如果让我给超人加段代码，我一定会用这些积木，大概是这样的（这也是我留的作业哦 ！我待会儿会发代码，但小萌新能自己做出来吗？提示：用到了变量和广播哦！）：<iframe src=\"https://ide.codemao.cn/we/559277\" width=\"640\" height=\"498\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></iframe></p>\n<p>亮代码：</p>\n<p>超人代码：<img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/Fm7x2kOd_19Q3JB6eavZ_lRX6lQd\"></p>\n<p>按钮代码：<img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FmO0ErYk1HwU6dFpHciqW9ttL0n-\"></p>\n<p>“救命啊”代码：<img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FmwLBvPKKWAT46-GBhLzKBLzHj5W\"></p>\n<p>背景就不亮了吧！</p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1492319799,"created_at":1492319799,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"18928","user":{"id":"179233","nickname":"杰鸽","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/Fj9WL32g3J_9Om1sWroOWquXZ25U","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>继上文</p>\n<p>9.10.11.12一起来</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FqUP9TpseT2G8pUvJk5P0jg3t_wo\"></p>\n<p>字面上都很好理解，但是一定要区分。可以看看：链接<span>:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pan.baidu.com/s/1eSoWEH0&nbsp;\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://pan.baidu.com/s/1eSoWEH0&nbsp;</a></span></p>\n<p><span>密码:&nbsp;7rae</span></p>\n<p><span>最后啰嗦一句：Y坐标是上下移动（如果Y坐标增加0，角色上下不一动；</span>如果Y坐标增加正数，角色向上移动；如果Y坐标增加一个负数，角色向下移动<span>）x坐标是左右移动（</span>如果X坐标增加0，角色左右不一动；如果X坐标增加正数，角色向右移动；如果X坐标增加一个负数，角色向左移动<span>）</span></p>\n<p><br></p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1492317744,"created_at":1492317744,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"18925","user":{"id":"129033","nickname":"空气戏","avatar_url":"https://cdn-community.codemao.cn/47/community/d2ViXzEwMDFfMTI5MDMzXzEyOTAzM18xNjEyNjY0MDY4NjEzX2I5N2JiZWU0.jpeg","subject_id":3798,"work_shop_name":"GEG工作室","work_shop_level":4,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FlSXhftozyDKTScnt5kCMPmeAulX\"></p>\n<p></p>\n<p><font size=\"7\" color=\"#ff0000\">文字印章，就是某个字或某个英文。大小也是可以设置的。同样的，这个积木也要先使用落笔才可以使用。</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"7\" color=\"#00ff00\">===================</font></p>\n<p><br></p>","n_comments":1,"updated_at":1492315212,"created_at":1492315212,"earliest_comments":[{"id":"479142","user":{"id":"5831853","nickname":"某个普通用户","avatar_url":"https://static-platform.codemao.cn/avatar/default/v1_user_004.png","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"不用蜡笔也可以使用","created_at":1589087514}]},{"id":"18924","user":{"id":"129033","nickname":"空气戏","avatar_url":"https://cdn-community.codemao.cn/47/community/d2ViXzEwMDFfMTI5MDMzXzEyOTAzM18xNjEyNjY0MDY4NjEzX2I5N2JiZWU0.jpeg","subject_id":3798,"work_shop_name":"GEG工作室","work_shop_level":4,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FoSMAHufCXTv5rE2-YMVeraeccqA\"></p>\n<p><font size=\"7\" color=\"#ff0000\">增加画笔粗细，这个值也同样是可以调整的，你作画用的笔的字迹大小，就是画笔粗细。</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"7\" color=\"#00ff00\">===================</font></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1492315191,"created_at":1492315191,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"18923","user":{"id":"129033","nickname":"空气戏","avatar_url":"https://cdn-community.codemao.cn/47/community/d2ViXzEwMDFfMTI5MDMzXzEyOTAzM18xNjEyNjY0MDY4NjEzX2I5N2JiZWU0.jpeg","subject_id":3798,"work_shop_name":"GEG工作室","work_shop_level":4,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/Ft5e0H-UAlBv_s6im-j8Mj502M3j\"></p>\n<p><font size=\"7\" color=\"#ff0000\">颜色值，这个词可能难理解，但我们可以忽略不计。这样就变成了设置画笔（一种颜色），这样是不是就容易理解的多了？</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"7\" color=\"#00ff00\">===================</font></p>\n<p><br></p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1492315171,"created_at":1492315171,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"18922","user":{"id":"129033","nickname":"空气戏","avatar_url":"https://cdn-community.codemao.cn/47/community/d2ViXzEwMDFfMTI5MDMzXzEyOTAzM18xNjEyNjY0MDY4NjEzX2I5N2JiZWU0.jpeg","subject_id":3798,"work_shop_name":"GEG工作室","work_shop_level":4,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FjUKWgYiyl3i3macjTq9GvlEc0kF\"></p>\n<p><font size=\"7\" color=\"#ff0000\">设置画笔粗细，这个值是可以调整的，你作画用的笔的字迹大小，就是画笔粗细。系统默认的画笔粗细是1。</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"7\" color=\"#00ff00\">===================</font></p>\n<p><br></p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1492315146,"created_at":1492315146,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"18921","user":{"id":"129033","nickname":"空气戏","avatar_url":"https://cdn-community.codemao.cn/47/community/d2ViXzEwMDFfMTI5MDMzXzEyOTAzM18xNjEyNjY0MDY4NjEzX2I5N2JiZWU0.jpeg","subject_id":3798,"work_shop_name":"GEG工作室","work_shop_level":4,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/Fn80bBBeAzKSDfo7v7J6GUuIP89c\"></p>\n<p><span>清除画笔，一瞬间把所作的画全部清除。</span></p>\n<p><span><font color=\"#00ff00\">===================</font></span><br></p>\n<p><br></p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1492315125,"created_at":1492315125,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"18920","user":{"id":"129033","nickname":"空气戏","avatar_url":"https://cdn-community.codemao.cn/47/community/d2ViXzEwMDFfMTI5MDMzXzEyOTAzM18xNjEyNjY0MDY4NjEzX2I5N2JiZWU0.jpeg","subject_id":3798,"work_shop_name":"GEG工作室","work_shop_level":4,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FgA8GKEDBb4A3ZRkK_cUomgxbRxC\"></p>\n<p><font size=\"7\" color=\"#ff0000\">顾名思义，就是把笔抬起来，停止作画。</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"7\" color=\"#00ff00\">===================</font></p>\n<p><br></p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1492315091,"created_at":1492315091,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"18919","user":{"id":"129033","nickname":"空气戏","avatar_url":"https://cdn-community.codemao.cn/47/community/d2ViXzEwMDFfMTI5MDMzXzEyOTAzM18xNjEyNjY0MDY4NjEzX2I5N2JiZWU0.jpeg","subject_id":3798,"work_shop_name":"GEG工作室","work_shop_level":4,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FskSScNb_OOTMg9RQy3aq4MVootb\"><br></p>\n<p><font color=\"#ff0000\" size=\"7\">顾名思义，就是把笔放下，开始作画。这个积木是全部作画积木的基本积木。如果没有这个积木，那么是做不出画的。</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"7\" color=\"#00ff00\">===================</font></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1492315051,"created_at":1492315051,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"18896","user":{"id":"179233","nickname":"杰鸽","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/Fj9WL32g3J_9Om1sWroOWquXZ25U","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>继上文</p>\n<p>7.<img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FroheTmN2Khoj8vIrZgz2u-zJEXw\"></p>\n<p>8.<img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/Fm0v-7RcglCYvdapKYted7oiMSbZ\"></p>\n<p>分析：为什么把它们放在一起讲呢？因为它们差不多。只有一点不一样。</p>\n<p>7强调结果（最后到达某一个坐标点，颇像科幻小说里的瞬移），8强调过程（怎么到达的），效果也不一样。例如：一样是把滑稽从X:0 Y:0的位置移动到X:255 Y：12的位置，先看看7的效果：<iframe src=\"https://ide.codemao.cn/we/558372\" width=\"640\" height=\"498\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></iframe></p>\n<p>再看看8的效果：<iframe src=\"https://ide.codemao.cn/we/558367\" width=\"640\" height=\"498\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></iframe></p>\n<p>领悟了吗？</p>\n<p>另外，8的运动轨迹是线段（两点之间线段最短），设定的时间越长，速度越慢（路程一定，速度与时间成反比例关系）</p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1492309497,"created_at":1492309497,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"18892","user":{"id":"179233","nickname":"杰鸽","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/Fj9WL32g3J_9Om1sWroOWquXZ25U","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>继上文</p>\n<p>聪明办法就是用这个积木：</p>\n<p>6.<img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FksJeHpRK1wzZ6fRmSeu6zsIQcPm\"></p>\n<p>分析：直接获得学员到教官的角度，其实就是上文的plus版。</p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1492308778,"created_at":1492308778,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"18891","user":{"id":"179233","nickname":"杰鸽","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/Fj9WL32g3J_9Om1sWroOWquXZ25U","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>继上文</p>\n<p>5.<img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/Fk4FIIPcJAqOkYbKXFm-mp7k0x3h\"></p>\n<p>分析：和旋转90度差不多。但是，如果给旋转90度和面向90度加上无限循环，前者会有上文那样炫酷的特效，而后者跟没使用差不多...面向90度其实就是让角色向90度看去。<iframe src=\"https://ide.codemao.cn/we/558300\" width=\"640\" height=\"498\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></iframe></p>\n<p>这是怎么做到的？有两种方法（聪明办法和笨办法），笨办法就是想方设法知道学员与教官的角度，然后挨个设置。聪明办法就是...</p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1492308674,"created_at":1492308674,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"18888","user":{"id":"179233","nickname":"杰鸽","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/Fj9WL32g3J_9Om1sWroOWquXZ25U","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>继上文</p>\n<p>补充一下旋转（）度</p>\n<p>旋转的样子是根据中心点而设定的，那什么是中心点呢？</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FuQ9sN3jAQzxLVeHUq87FyxC3xeF\"><br></p>\n<p>这就是中心点按钮，旋转是围绕着中心点进行旋转的！</p>\n<p>玩个游戏：<iframe src=\"https://ide.codemao.cn/we/159519\" width=\"700\" height=\"500\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></iframe></p>\n<p>在这个游戏中，是怎么导致了小球这样转动呢，翻代码也没看出什么特点，玄机就藏在：它的中心点设在这里：<img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FtvoFWjBAgff87F0XZSF8TTYKQyZ\"></p>\n<p>角色的外面！这样就会有如此效果：<iframe src=\"https://ide.codemao.cn/we/558234\" width=\"700\" height=\"500\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></iframe></p>\n<p>加以修改，还可以做出太阳系的星球公转、自转。</p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1492308029,"created_at":1492308029,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"18885","user":{"id":"179233","nickname":"杰鸽","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/Fj9WL32g3J_9Om1sWroOWquXZ25U","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>继上文</p>\n<p>4.<img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FoPkXpVUuCUlfOHW9U8QBa0dNkPi\"></p>\n<p>分析：当角色碰到舞台边缘，会改变运动方向（一般就是头朝下，脚朝上的尴尬场面。想要缓解尴尬最好的方式就是把角色的旋转方式改为左右旋转。但最好不要用改变旋转方向的积木，需要在这里改才能一直是左右翻转：<img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FnC-BpCXMhNwW9mUJBnDBp9AJMIW\"><span>）</span></p>\n<p>建议配合重复执行使用（否则只能弹一次。）。</p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1492307172,"created_at":1492307172,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"18884","user":{"id":"179233","nickname":"杰鸽","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/Fj9WL32g3J_9Om1sWroOWquXZ25U","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>继上文</p>\n<p>3.<img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/Fr-eLptWdMeEUYBlYXKi9bv83TsZ\"></p>\n<p>分析：这个怎么解释呢？也没什么技术含量，经常用来表示角色受到攻击或神情兴奋。如<img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FrQwmeq96KHMmhp9plod62RSbNrz\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/Fld_hDYe7cyQMAUWhQYHL_uF1DwS\"><iframe src=\"https://ide.codemao.cn/we/558170\" width=\"640\" height=\"498\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></iframe><br></p>\n<p><br></p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1492306842,"created_at":1492306842,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"18883","user":{"id":"179233","nickname":"杰鸽","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/Fj9WL32g3J_9Om1sWroOWquXZ25U","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>继上文</p>\n<p>2.<img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FiSFrGlXOhheRMqjsLDtqqQ-TdYq\"></p>\n<p>字面上就很好理解了。有个小妙用上过公开课的同学应该知道：<img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FoRH-bAFwp8vnbyQyBdoK4bJPqT6\"></p>\n<p>看效果：<iframe src=\"https://ide.codemao.cn/we/558170\" width=\"640\" height=\"498\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></iframe></p>\n<p><br></p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1492306452,"created_at":1492306452,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"18882","user":{"id":"179233","nickname":"杰鸽","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/Fj9WL32g3J_9Om1sWroOWquXZ25U","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>继上文</p>\n<p>看积木：</p>\n<p>1.<img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FmElFFSSbyYsAl7Wg2v5qDPZ2t1R\"></p>\n<p>相当于Y坐标增加10，也可理解为角色向右移动10个长度单位。最好理解的方式就是：这个角色向右走10步。配合外观积木可以让角色动起来！<img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FtKKJVh-DJ3nLGZagUJRLrcgJRqU\"></p>\n<p>效果：<iframe src=\"https://ide.codemao.cn/we/558149\" width=\"640\" height=\"498\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></iframe></p>\n<p><br></p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1492306108,"created_at":1492306108,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"18881","user":{"id":"179233","nickname":"杰鸽","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/Fj9WL32g3J_9Om1sWroOWquXZ25U","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>继上文</p>\n<p>简单说。编程猫平台只有XY两种坐标轴（平面），但是代码岛（立体）有多了一个Z坐标，这是因为编程猫平台是2D的，代码岛偏向3D的——这就犹如原来正方形只有长和宽，可以算面积、周长；现在是正方体，有长、宽、高，可以算密度、体积、表面积、溶积……等等等等。</p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1492305735,"created_at